{"title":"Veolo Launches Kickstarter for their Veolo 2.0 Bike Trailer","link":"https://theradavist.com/veolo-2-0-bike-trailer-kickstarter","date":1779890661000,"content":"<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/veolo-bike-trailer\" target=\"_blank\">Veolo</a> completely reworked their trailer from the ground up with its 2.0 version, and they think you’ll really like where it ended up. All the feedback gathered over the past three years, combined with their own experience using it, pushed Veolo to revisit pretty much every single detail. The goal was to make it lighter, more versatile, and even more fun to ride aggressively off-road.</em></p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-1.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-1.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-1.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-1.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>It’s no longer just a trailer — it has become a full modular system with a growing range of add-ons.</p>\n<p>The idea behind Veolo has always been to create a trailer that doesn’t feel like a compromise, but like a natural extension of the bike itself. Something equally suited for everyday cargo, outdoor trips, and sporty riding.</p>\n<p>After the first series and almost one year of development, it became the Veolo 2.0.<br />\n<img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1250\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-8.jpg 2000w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-8-1200x750.jpg 1200w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-8-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-8-768x480.jpg 768w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-8-1998x1249.jpg 1998w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1333\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-9.jpg 1333w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-9-533x800.jpg 533w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-9-682x1024.jpg 682w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-9-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-9-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1249\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-7.jpg 2000w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-7-1200x749.jpg 1200w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-7-1536x959.jpg 1536w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-7-768x480.jpg 768w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-7-1998x1248.jpg 1998w\" /></p>\n<h3>Veolo 2.0 Quick Hits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Only 6.7 kg weight with up to 60 kg payload</li>\n<li>Patented single-wheel suspension for stable handling on rough terrain</li>\n<li>Self-regulating, replaceable elastomer suspension</li>\n<li>Modular magnetic mounting system for different add-ons</li>\n<li>Ultralight one-click hitch</li>\n<li>Fully disassemblable for compact transport and storage</li>\n<li>High-strength AL6061 aluminum frame</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-2.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-2.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-3.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-3.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/05/2026_Veolo_2.0-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The system is built to cover a huge range of use cases — from daily cargo and bikepacking setups to dog transport and long-load applications up to 3.5 m for watersports gear.</p>\n<p>For Johann personally, this project has become a real long-term obsession. Countless prototypes, iterations, and test kilometers went into getting it to this point.</p>\n<p>Veolo is launching the <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/veolo/veolo-trailer-20-modular-high-performance-bike-trailer\" target=\"_blank\">Kickstarter campaign</a> on today to finally bring the first production series to life together with the community.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/veolo-2-0-bike-trailer-kickstarter\">Veolo Launches Kickstarter for their Veolo 2.0 Bike Trailer</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://cms.theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"spencer harding","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"d2c1845b234910423499834ff7a0e62766263094deeb69eb933851ebf56afc80","category":"Cycling"}